name: Strings for Electric Guitar
description: Perfectly balanced strings that are highly pleasant to play and boast tuning precision and a bright sound with extreme durability.

name: Strings for Classical Guitar
description: Guitarists will find this set provides a warm sweetness with more edge than when paired with the SN Nylon strings.

name: Violin Strings
description: While developing our violin string we have received positive assessments that our Platinum E-string allows for new dimensions in violin playing.

name: Guitar bridge
description: The design of this bridge allows a adjustment. It is not only adjustable in terms of height and intonation, but also individual string spacing.

name: Guitar Strap
description: The padding is made out of little cells filled with air. The air padding makes your instrument feel lighter. Our shoulder straps are made from elastic.

name: Guitar Machine Heads
description: With its cutting edge Velvet-Tec technology it is the ultimate combination of tasteful design and velvet-smooth feel and touch.

name: Guitar Capo
description: Professional capo for nearly all six and twelve string guitars with flat or slightly curved fingerboards.
